column1: ## Stellar spectra for Roman Slitless Spectroscopy Data Challenge 2: Group 00
## Spectra generated from interpolating the grid of PHOENIX spectral
## library using pysynphot. The astrophysical parameters are taken randomly
## from the Gaia Data Release 3 golden sample of astrophysical parameters
## (Creevey et al. 2023). The tables are joined with the distance catalogue
## of Bailer-Jones et al. 2021. Only sources fainter than G = 17
## are taken
